simple-git

A lightweight interface for running git commands in any node.js application.

Installation

npm install simple-git --save

Usage

const git = simpleGit();

// Example: Check if a repo is a repo
const isRepo = await git.checkIsRepo();

// Example: Clone a repo
await git.clone(REPO_URL, LOCAL_PATH);

// Example: Get commit log
const log = await git.log();
console.log(log.latest.hash);
